# Always Test When Making Changes

**Important:** When you make changes to this codebase, always run the test suite afterward to catch regressions.

## How to Test

```bash
tox run -e py
```

Or run both py and lint:

```bash
tox run
```

## When to Test

- After editing Python source in `src/desk/`
- After adding or changing tests
- After modifying `pyproject.toml` (deps, scripts, tox config)
- Before considering a change complete

## Note to Self

If you are an AI agent working on this project: run `tox run -e py` after every change and fix any failing tests before finishing.
